- sink: `u32 count = gf_list_count(pck->stream->program->streams);`

The sink is at line 1055 which is inside m2tsdmx_on_event for GF_M2TS_EVT_PES_PCR event. But wait, that event is triggered from line 1807, not from gf_m2ts_section_complete.

Hmm, let me re-read the code in gf_m2ts_section_complete. Looking at line 1313:```c
else if (ts->on_event) {
    GF_M2TS_SL_PCK pck;
    pck.data_len = sec->length;
